#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"Praise is a powerful parenting skill.\n"
"\n"
"If we praise our teens when they do something well, we will see them do more and more positive things!"
msgstr ""
"Kipindi cha leo ni kuhusu Kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Kusifia ni ujuzi wenye nguvu katika malezi.\n"
"\n"
"Kama tutawasifia vijana wetu wanapofanya jambo vizuri, tutawaona wakifanya mambo mazuri zaidi na zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will praise help you and your family? Tap play to find out!"
msgstr "Jinsi gani kusifia itasakusaidia na familia yako? Gusa cheza ili kujua!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic today is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"It is good to praise our children when they've done good because when we do that, they will do more of that good behavior we want to see.\n"
"\n"
"And let's not forget to praise ourselves when we do good!"
msgstr ""
"Habari zenu?\n"
"\n"
"Kipindi chetu ya leo inahusu kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni vizuri kuwasifia watoto wetu wanapofanya vizuri kwa sababu tunapofanya hivyo, watazidi kuifanya tabia nzuri tunayotaka kuiona.\n"
"\n"
"Na tusisahau pia kujisifia sisi wenyewe tunapofanya mazuri!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise is an easy way to build your teen’s confidence and strengthen your connection. It really works!"
msgstr "Kusifia ni njia rahisi kujenga kujiamini kwa kijana wako na kuimarisha uhusiano wenu. Inafanya kazi kweli!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise works, but it’s not always easy. Hear how @data.characters.media_female_2.name started using it at home"
msgstr "Kusifia kunafanya kazi, lakini siyo rahisi daima. Sikiliza jinsi @data.characters.media_female_2.name alivyoanza kuitumia nyumbani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we learnt about this praising thing I thought, “We were never praised for things as teenagers, so why should we start now?” But I got interested when I learnt what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after the weekly workshop, I noticed my teen doing what they do every day: washing the dishes. And I said “Thank you for washing the dishes, my girl, it really makes me happy that you are helping out.” My teen was smiling and she even came to give me a hug, which she never does.\n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget sometimes or give praise at the same time as criticism. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!When we learnt about this praising thing I thought, “We were never praised for things as teenagers, so why should we start now?” But I got interested when I learnt what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after the weekly workshop, I noticed my teen doing what they do every day: washing the dishes. And I said “Thank you for washing the dishes, my girl, it really makes me happy that you are helping out.” My teen was smiling and she even came to give me a hug, which she never does.\n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget sometimes or give praise at the same time as criticism. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!"
msgstr ""
"Tulipojifunza kuhusu suala hili la kusifia, nilifikiri, “Sisi hatukuwahi kusifiwa tulipokuwa vijana, kwa hiyo kwa nini tuanze sasa?” Lakini nilivutiwa nilipojua manufaa ya kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Mara tu baada ya kipindi cha kila wiki, nilimwona mwana wangu akifanya kile anachofanya kila siku: kuosha vyombo. Nikamwambia, “Asante kwa kuosha vyombo, mwana wangu, inanifurahisha kweli kuona unasaidia nyumbani.” Mwana wangu alitabasamu na hata alikuja kunikumbatia, jambo ambalo hafanyi kamwe.\n"
"\n"
"Hili suala la kusifia ni gumu. Bado husahau wakati mwingine au nasema sifa huku nikikosoa pia. Lakini kusifia kweli kunaleta tofauti. Sikuamini kwamba sifa rahisi tu ingeweza kumletea mtu mabadiliko makubwa namna hiyo!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on our own experience with praise."
msgstr "Ebu tujikumbushe kwenye uzoefu wetu wa kusifia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think about the last time someone thanked you, or said you did something great.\n"
"\n"
"How did it make you feel?"
msgstr ""
"Fikiria kuhusu mara ya mwisho mtu alipokushukuru, au alipokuambia umefanya kitu fulani kizuri sana.\n"
"\n"
"Ilikufanya ujisikieje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We sometimes have to get used to being praised and praising others. That’s okay."
msgstr "Sisi wakati mwingine tunatakiwa kuzoea kusifiwa na kusifia wengine. Hiyo ni sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel happy."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s great! Being praised often makes us feel proud."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Parents usually do not get thanked or praised enough.\n"
"\n"
"How does it make you feel when nobody says \"thank you\"?"
msgstr ""
"Mara nyingi Wazazi hawapewi shukrani au kusifia vya kutosha.\n"
"\n"
"Unajisikiaje pale ambapo hakuna mtu anakamia \"asante\"?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Huzuni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Hasira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tired"
msgstr "Kuchoka"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your teen can feel this way too. That's what makes this week's parenting tool simple but important: Praise them for what they do right."
msgstr "Kijana wako anaweza pia kujisikia hivyo. Hicho ndicho kinachofanya nyenzo ya malezi ya wiki hii iwe rahisi lakini muhimu: Msifie anapofanya vizuri."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Praise really is powerful.\n"
"\n"
"Let’s look at the example of @data.characters.f1_mother.name and her daughters:"
msgstr ""
"Kusifia kuna nguvu sana.\n"
"\n"
"Hebu tuangalie mfano wa @data.characters.f1_mother.name na mabinti zake:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When @data.characters.f1_mother.name is busy, her two daughters often fight. But today, her older daughter actually helped her sister with her schoolwork!"
msgstr "Pindi @data.characters.f1_mother.name anapotingwa na shughuli, mara nyingi mabinti zake wawili hupigana. Lakini leo, binti yake mkubwa alimsaidia mdogo wake kufanya kazi yake ya shule!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name,
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for doing your schoolwork, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name, and thank you for helping your sister, @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name. I'm so proud of you!"
msgstr "Asante kwa kufanya kazi zako za shule, @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name na asante kwa kumsadia mdogo wako, @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name najivunia nyie!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is time for some questions!"
msgstr "Sasa ni muda wa kuuliza maswali!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How did praise make @data.characters.f1_mother.name's teens feel?"
msgstr "Je, kusifia kuliwafanya vijana wa @data.characters.f1_mother.name wajisikieje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay"
msgstr "Sawa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try again! Praise often creates positive feelings, like feeling happy or proud."
msgstr "Jaribu tena! Kusifia hutengeneza hisia chanya kama kujihisi mwenye furaha au kujivunia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Furaha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Kujivunia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. Praise made them feel happy and proud!"
msgstr "Hiyo ni sahihi. Kusifia kunawafanya wajihisi furaha na kujivunia!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why did she praise them?"
msgstr "Kwa nini aliwasifia?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To get them to do it more often"
msgstr "Ili kuwafanya wazidi kufanya hivyo mara nyingi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help her finish her work"
msgstr "Kumsaidia amalize kazi yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To make them feel good"
msgstr "Ili kuwafanya wajisikie vizuri"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To make herself feel good"
msgstr "Ili yeye mwenyewe ajisikie vizuri"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"All of those things are true!\n"
"\n"
"When her teens are happy, @data.characters.f1_mother.name feels happy. And she got her work done."
msgstr ""
"Mambo yote hayo ni ya kweli!\n"
"\n"
"Pindi vijana wake wanapofurahi, @data.characters.f1_mother.name hujisikia furaha. Na aliweza kufanya kazi zake."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Here are some skills to help you praise your teens.\n"
"You can also praise other adults in your household, too. Notice how they respond!"
msgstr ""
"Huu hapa ni baadhi ya ujuzi wa kukusaidia kusifia vijana wako.\n"
"Unaweza pia kusifia watu wazima nyumbani kwako, vilevile. Gundua jins wanavyoitikia!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr "ONA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look for anything your teen does that is helpful or good and praise them for it. They may not show it, but you will see them doing that good thing again. It will also reassure them that you notice and care."
msgstr "Tafuta kitu chochote anachofanya kijana wako kwa ajili ya kusaidia au kilicho kizuri na umsifie kwa kitu hicho. Anaweza asioneshe furaha yake, lakini utamwona akifanya tena kitu hicho kizuri. Pia itamthibitishia kuwa unatambua anachokifanya na unajali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr "SEMA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Be enthusiastic – really mean it when you say it!"
msgstr "Onyesha shauku – unaposema jambo, liseme kwa moyo wa dhati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REPEAT IT"
msgstr "RUDIA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try to find something to thank them for every day. Even something really small."
msgstr "Jaribu kutafuta kitu cha kukufanya umshukuru kila siku. Hata kitu kidogo sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It can be hard to think of reasons to praise your teen! Here are some ideas from other parents:"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine ni vigumu kufikiria kitu gani cha kumsifia kijana wako! Haya ni mawazo kutoka kwa wazazi wengine:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Thank you for...**\n"
"- Being kind to someone\n"
"- Cleaning your room\n"
"- Joining a family meal\n"
"- Greeting other family members\n"
"- Looking after your siblings\n"
"- Coming home on time\n"
"- Showing thoughtfulness\n"
"- Saying 'please' or 'thank you'\n"
"- Going to school on time\n"
"- Doing chores or schoolwork"
msgstr ""
"**Asante kwa...**\n"
"- Kuwa mkarimu kwa mtu fulani\n"
"- Kusafisha chumba chako\n"
"- Kujiunga katika chakula cha familia\n"
"- Kusalimia wanafamilia wengine\n"
"- Kuwaangalia wadogo zako\n"
"- Kurudi nyumbani kwa wakati\n"
"- Kuonyesha unafikiria\n"
"- Kusema “tafadhali” au “asante”\n"
"- Kwenda shule kwa wakati\n"
"- Kufanya kazi za nyumbani au kazi za shule"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This week's home activity is to praise your teen once a day. It will only take 10 seconds!"
msgstr "Zoezi la nyumbani la wiki hii ni kumsifia kijana wako mara moja kwa siku. Utatumia sekunde 10 tu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you praise your teen once a day this week?"
msgstr "Unaweza kumsifia kijana wako mara moja kwa siku kwa wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who practise praise at home get better results!"
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Wazazi wanaofanya zoezi la kusifia nyumbani wanapata Matokeo mazuri zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try praising your teen for something simple at first, like looking after their siblings or going to school."
msgstr "Unaweza kufanya! Jaribu kumsifia kijana wako kwa kitu rahisi mwanzoni, kwa kuwaangalia wdago zake a kwa kwenda shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. With time, giving praise will become easier. Try to praise yourself for something first, like \"Good job using @global.app_name. It shows you care.\""
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa. Baada ya muda, kusifia itakuwa rahisi zaidi. Jaribu kujisifia mwenyewe kwa kitu flani kwanza, kama \"Kazi nzuri @global.app_name. Huonesha unajari\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, praise is a powerful tool. The more attention you give to positive behaviour, the more positive behaviour you will see."
msgstr "Kumbuka, kusifia ni nyenzo yenye nguvu. Kadri unavyoweka umakini zaidi kwenye tabia chanya, ndivyo utakavyoona zaidi tabia chanya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear from @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name on how it feels to get praise from her mother"
msgstr "Sikia kutoka @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name jinsi anavyojisikia aliposifiwa na mama yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I was grateful that my mother learnt about praise.\n"
"\n"
"My mother always noticed when I was doing something wrong. She would shout at me and hit me.\n"
"\n"
"But when my mother did the workshop, she would praise me for little things. First I thought “What is going on?” but then it continued. I liked it so I did more good things I thought she would like.\n"
"\n"
"It feels great that my mother sees the good things I do, and not just the bad things.\n"
"\n"
"I even said it to her once. During one-on-one time, I said “Thank you, mom, for saying something nice when I do things well, not only when I do things wrong.” This made us both very happy."
msgstr ""
"Nilishukuru kwamba Mama yangu alijifunza kuhusu kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Mama yangu mara nyingi aligundua pindi nilipofanya kitu kibaya. Alikuwa akinifokea na kunipiga.\n"
"\n"
"Lakini Mama yangu alipohudhuria warsha, alinisifia kwa vitu vidogo. Mwanzoni niliwaza \" Nini kinaendelea?\"lakini kiliendelea. Nilikipenda hivyo niliendelea kufanya mambo mazuri zaidi na nilifikiri atapenda.\n"
"\n"
"Najihisi furaha kwamba Mama yangu anaona vitu vizuri ninavyofanya, na si mambo mabaya tu.\n"
"\n"
"Niliwahi kumwambia mara moja. Wakati tunatumia muda wa pamoja wawili, nilisema \" Asante Mama, kwa kuniambia maneno mazuri wakati ninapofanya Jambo vyema, na si tu wakati ninapofanya jambo vibaya.\" Hii ilitufanya sote kuwa na furaha sana."

